					text: 'Most of us would agree – mornings are hectic. Getting yourself and possibly others ready for the day ahead may...'
				}).wow.slideInDown
				+post-classic({
					img: 'post-2-370x239',
					time: {
						datetime: '2020-08-09',
						datetext: 'August 9, 2020'
					},
					title: 'How to Make Your Breakfast Easy and Yummy',
					text: 'Overloading your breakfast with calories may not be the best idea but when you need a boost for the upcoming...'
				}).wow.slideInUp
				+post-classic({
